\c 6
\s Jesu anoshovorwa paNazareta
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakabvapo, akasvika kunyika yekwake; vadzidzi vake vakamutevera.
\v 2 Zvino rava sabata, akatanga kudzidzisa musinagoge; vazhinji vaka\add mu\add*nzwa, vakashamisika vachiti: Izvi zvinobvepi kwaari? Injere dzipi dzakapiwa kwaari, kuti nemabasa esimba akadai anoitwa nemaoko ake?
\v 3 Uyu haasi muvezi here, mwanakomana waMaria, nemukoma waJakobho naJose naJudha naSimoni? Nehanzvadzi dzake hadzisi pano nesu here? Vakagumburwa naye.
\v 4 Asi Jesu akati kwavari: Muporofita haangashaiwi kukudzwa, kunze kwemunyika yekwake, nepakati pehama, nemumba make.
\v 5 Akasagona kubata chero basa resimba ipapo, kunze kwekuti wakaisa maoko pamusoro pevairwara vashoma, akaporesa.
\v 6 Akashamisika nekusatenda kwavo. Uye akapota-pota nemisha achidzidzisa.
\s Vanegumi nevaviri vanotumwa kunoparidza nekuporesa
\p
\v 7 Zvino wakadanira kwaari vanegumi nevaviri, akatanga kuvatuma vaviri-vaviri, akavapa simba pamusoro pemweya yetsvina.
\v 8 Akavaraira kuti varege kutora chinhu cherwendo kunze kwemudonzvo chete; kwete chikwama, kwete chingwa, kwete mari mubhanhire.
\v 9 Asi vafuke manyatera, varege kupfeka nguvo mbiri.
\v 10 Zvino akati kwavari: Pose pamunopinda mumba, mugaremo kusvikira muchibvapo.
\v 11 Asi vose vasingakugamuchiriyi kana kukunzwai, kana muchibvapo, zuzai guruva riri pasi petsoka dzenyu, chive chapupu kwavari. Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Zvicharerukira Sodhoma kana Gomora nezuva rekutongwa kupfuura guta iro.
\v 12 Vakati vabuda, vakaparidza kuti vatendeuke;
\v 13 zvino vakabudisa madhimoni mazhinji, vakazodza nemafuta vazhinji vairwara, vachiporesa.
\s Kuurawa kwaJohwani Mubhabhatidzi
\p
\v 14 Mambo Herodhe ndoku\add zvi\add*nzwa, nokuti zita rake rakava pachena, akati: Johwani anobhabhatidza akamutswa kubva kuvakafa, naizvozvo masimba anobata maari.
\v 15 Vamwe vakati: NdiEria; nevamwe vakati: Muporofita, kana \add wakaita\add* seumwe wevaporofita.
\v 16 Asi Herodhe wakati anzwa, akati: Uyu ndiJohwani uya wandakagura ini musoro; iye wamuka kubva kuvakafa.
\p
\v 17 Nokuti Herodhe pachake wakange atuma \add vanhu\add* akabata Johwani, akamusunga mutirongo nekuda kwaHerodhiasi, mukadzi waFiripi, munin'ina wake; nokuti \add Herodhe\add* wakange amuwana.
\v 18 Nokuti Johwani wakange ati kuna Herodhe: Hauna kutenderwa kuti uve nemukadzi wemunin'ina wako.
\v 19 Herodhiasi akamuvenga nechemumoyo, akada kumuuraya, asi wakakonewa;
\v 20 Nokuti Herodhe aitya Johwani, achiziva kuti murume wakarurama, mutsvene, akamuchengetedza. Zvino paakamunzwa akaita zvinhu zvakawanda, akamunzwa nemufaro.
\p
\v 21 Asi zuva rakafanira rakati rasvika, Herodhe nezuva rekuberekwa kwake akaitira chirairo madzishe ake nevatungamiriri vezvuru nevatungamiriri veGarirea,
\v 22 zvino mukunda waHerodhiasi uyo paakapinda akatamba, akafadza Herodhe nevakange vagere pakudya naye; mambo akati kumusikana: Kumbira kwandiri chipi zvacho chaunoda, ndigokupa.
\v 23 Zvino akamupikira \add achiti\add*: Chero chii chaunokumbira kwandiri ndichakupa, kusvikira pahafu yeushe hwangu.
\v 24 Akabuda akati kuna mai vake: Ndichakumbirei? Vakati: Musoro waJohwani Mubhabhatidzi.
\v 25 Pakarepo akakurumidza kupinda kuna mambo, akakumbira achiti: Ndinoda kuti mundipe mundiro ikozvino musoro waJohwani Mubhabhatidzi.
\v 26 Mambo akashungurudzika zvikuru, \add asi \add*nekuda kwemhiko, nekwevakange vagere naye pakudya, wakange asingadi kumurambira.
\v 27 Pakarepo mambo akatuma mhondi, akaraira kuti musoro wake uuyiswe. Akaenda, akamugura musoro mutirongo,
\v 28 akauya nemusoro wake mundiro, akaupa kumusikana, musikana ndokuupa mai vake.
\v 29 Vadzidzi vake vakati vachi\add zvi\add*nzwa, vakauya vakatora chitunha chake, vakachiisa muguva.
\s Vanezvuru zvishanu vanopiwa kudya naJesu
\p
\v 30 Zvino vaapositori vakaunganira kuna Jesu, vakamuudza zvose, nezvavakange vaita, nezvavakange vadzidzisa.
\v 31 Akati kwavari: Uyai imwi pachenyu moga kunzvimbo yerenje, muzorore zvishoma. Nokuti vaiva vazhinji vaiuya nekuenda, vakasava nemukana kunyange wekudya.
\v 32 Vakaenda nechikepe kunzvimbo yerenje vari vega.
\v 33 Zvaunga zvikavaona vachienda, uye vazhinji vakamuziva, vakamhanyirako pamwechete netsoka vachibva pamaguta ose, vakavatangira, vakasangana kwaari.
\p
\v 34 Zvino Jesu wakati achibuda, akaona chaunga chikuru, ndokuvanzwira tsitsi, nokuti vakange vakaita semakwai asina mufudzi; akatanga kuvadzidzisa zvinhu zvizhinji.
\p
\v 35 Zvino nguva yakati yaenda zvikuru, vadzidzi vake vakauya kwaari vakati: Iyi inzvimbo yerenje, uye nguva yatoenda;
\v 36 varegei, kuti vaende kuruwa rwakapoteredza nemisha vanozvitengera zvingwa; nokuti havana chavangadya.
\v 37 Akapindura akati kwavari: Vapei imwi kuti vadye. Vakati kwaari: Tingaenda here tinotenga zvingwa zvemadhenario* mazana maviri, tivape vadye?
\v 38 Akati kwavari: Mune zvingwa zvingani? Endai munoona. Vakati vaziva vakati: Zvishanu, nehove mbiri.
\v 39 Zvino akavaraira kuti vavagarise vose pasi nemapoka-mapoka pauswa unyoro.
\v 40 Zvino vakagara pasi nemapoka-mapoka nemazana uye nemakumi mashanu.
\v 41 Zvino wakati atora zvingwa zvishanu nehove mbiri, akatarira kumusoro kudenga, akavonga, akamedura zvingwa, akapa kuvadzidzi vake, kuti vazvigadzike pamberi pavo; nehove mbiri akavagovera vose.
\v 42 Zvino vakadya vose, vakaguta.
\v 43 Vakanunga matengu gumi nemaviri azere nezvimedu, nezvehove.
\v 44 Zvino avo vakadya zvingwa vaiva varume vanenge zvuru zvishanu.
\s Jesu anofamba pamusoro pemvura
\p
\v 45 Pakarepo akamanikidza vadzidzi vake kupinda muchikepe, vatungamire kuenda mhiri kuBhetisaidha, iye achirega chaunga chichienda.
\v 46 Akati avaoneka, akabva akaenda mugomo kunonyengetera.
\v 47 Zvino ava madekwani chikepe chakange chiri pakati pegungwa, iye ari oga panyika.
\v 48 Zvino wakavaona vachirwadziwa nekukwasva, nokuti mhepo yakange ichipesana navo; akauya kwavari nenguva inenge seyechina yekurinda yeusiku, achifamba pamusoro pegungwa; ndokuda kuvapfuura.
\v 49 Zvino vakati vachimuona achifamba pamusoro pegungwa, vakafunga kuti idzangaradzimu, vakaridza mhere.
\v 50 Nokuti vose vakamuona, vakavhunduka; asi pakarepo akataura navo, akati kwavari: Tsungai moyo, ndini, musatya.
\v 51 Akakwira kwavari muchikepe, mhepo ikanyarara; vakakatyamara zvikuru mukati mavo zvisingaverengeki, vakashamisika.
\v 52 Nokuti vakange vasina kunzwisisa zvezvingwa, nokuti moyo wavo wakange uri mukukutu.
\s Jesu anoporesa vanhu paGenesareti
\p
\v 53 Vakati vayambuka, vakasvika kunyika yeGenesareti, vakasungira chikepe pamahombekombe.
\v 54 Vakati vabuda muchikepe, pakarepo vakamuziva,
\v 55 vakamhanyira munharaunda iyo yose yakapoteredza, vakatanga kutenderera vakatakura vairwara pamichanja, kwavainzwa kuti ndiko kwaari.
\v 56 Zvino pose paakapinda pamisha kana pamaguta kana paruwa, vakaradzika varwere pamisika, vakamukumbira zvikuru kuti vabate mupendero wenguvo yake chete; uye vose vakamubata vakaponeswa.
